      <div class="model-card"><h3>Magic Chef 24" compact built-in</h3><p>European-sized compact wall oven for ADU + guest house + constrained apartment kitchens. Primary Magic Chef LA install base. Service: bake/broil element, thermostat, control, sensors, door.</p></div>
      <div class="model-card"><h3>Magic Chef 30" standard built-in</h3><p>Standard US-size wall oven at value-tier positioning. Rental property + institutional kitchen installations.</p></div>
      <div class="model-card"><h3>Self-clean cycle (where equipped)</h3><p>Not all Magic Chef wall oven models include self-clean. When present, standard pyrolytic with door-lock motor + thermal sensor service domain.</p></div>
      <div class="model-card"><h3>Convection (where equipped)</h3><p>Some Magic Chef wall ovens include convection at the higher-spec models. Service pattern standard: convection fan + element where applicable.</p></div>
